OL,3,CPlans to change school holidays in
OL,4,CWales are shelved
OL,6,FPlans to cut the school summer
OL,7,Fholidays in Wales have been shelved
OL,8,Funtil after the next Welsh Parliament
OL,9,Felection in 2026.
OL,11,FIt follows a mixed response from the
OL,12,Fbiggest Welsh Government education
OL,13,Fconsultation on record, which
OL,14,Fgenerated more than 16,000 responses
OL,15,Fand sought views on changing the
OL,16,Fschool calendar to spread school
OL,17,Fholidays out more evenly across the
OL,18,Fyear.
