OL,3,CPlans to change school holidays in
OL,4,CWales are shelved
OL,6,FIf the proposals had gone ahead, the
OL,7,Fhalf term break in October 2025 would
OL,8,Fhave been extended to a fortnight,
OL,9,Fwith a five-week rather than six-week
OL,10,Fholiday in summer 2026.
OL,12,FEducation secretary Lynne Neagle said
OL,13,Fpostponing the change until the next
OL,14,FSenedd term would allow schools to
OL,15,Ffocus on other major improvements.
