OL,3,CPlans to change school holidays in
OL,4,CWales are shelved
OL,6,FShe admitted "opinion was hugely
OL,7,Fdivided" on the issue, which had been
OL,8,Fstrongly opposed by teaching unions
OL,9,Fand as organisers of Wales' biggest
OL,10,Fagricultural show The Royal Welsh,
OL,11,Fplus some tourist attractions.
OL,13,FThe Welsh Government had said the
OL,14,Fproposal was to improve the education
OL,15,Fexperiences of young people,
OL,16,Fespecially the most disadvantaged, and
OL,17,Falign more effectively with how
OL,18,Ffamilies live and work.
