OL,6,F"I am acutely aware we are asking a
OL,7,Flot of teachers and schools. They are
OL,8,Fsupporting our ambitious
OL,9,Ftransformation of education in Wales
OL,10,Fand they need the time and the space
OL,11,Fto ensure these reforms deliver for
OL,12,Fchildren and young people.
OL,14,F"I want to prioritise ongoing school
OL,15,Freforms and improving attainment and
OL,16,Ftherefore, no changes will be made to
OL,17,Fthe school year this Senedd term.
